text: Ordered Sarawak laksa and kolo mee. Portion was generous and both tasted delicious! Service was good too.
Ordered liver soup, sarawak laksa and kolo mee dry....very authentic taste. If only they also include pork lard in the dry noodles.
Very authentic and delicious, for those who like to eat pork vermicelli and fruit strip soup. Must come😍👍
The service is very good, the environment is good, and the food is delicious. Not bad👍👍👍👍👍
